- [x] @italobusi : clean-up the YANG tree snapshots in section 2

> More debatably, the earlier I-D checked that the ends of the link had different uni which this does not AFAICT.  endpoint-id must be unique because it is a key but I think that there is no constraint on the uni leafref.  I do not know how to do that with a list of two elements but a YANG Doctor might.
